HP Remote DMM Display and Control
=====================================
This application is intended to provide a remote display and control facility for
the HP3478A Digital Multimeter via HPIB (GPIB).

The application requires an GPIB interface. The software was tested using a GPIB
interface buit using an Andruino board as described by Emanuale Girlando here:

http://egirland.blogspot.co.uk/2014/03/arduino-uno-as-usb-to-gpib-controller.html


